# agentme.cz — Cursor Rules

For full context see AGENTS.md in the repo root.

## Stack
- Astro 5, Tailwind CSS v4 (@tailwindcss/vite), anime.js v4, TypeScript strict
- Self-hosted Geist fonts via @fontsource-variable

## Key Rules

### Content
- ALL text lives in `src/data/content.ts` — never hardcode strings in components
- Tone: visionary manifesto, like Linear.app — no buzzwords, punchy copy

### Styling
- Tailwind v4 uses `@theme` directive in `src/styles/global.css` — no tailwind.config.js
- Dark mode only: bg #08090A, text #E8E8ED, accent gradient cyan #00D4FF → purple #7B61FF
- Section padding: 120-160px vertical, max-width 1200px centered

### Animations
- Use anime.js v4 modular imports: `import { animate, onScroll } from 'animejs'`
- Always add `prefers-reduced-motion` fallback (check window.matchMedia)
- Only animate `transform` and `opacity`
- Fade-in: 800ms easeOutExpo, stagger 100ms, scroll threshold 20%

### TypeScript
- Strict mode, no `any` types
- Component props use `interface Props { ... }`

### Performance
- Keep JS bundle under 50KB total
- No external font CDNs — self-hosted only
- Verify with `npm run build`

## Commands
```
npm run dev       # Dev server localhost:4321
npm run build     # Production build
npm run preview   # Preview build
```
